summary: Bigger Breeze Home, Adds another room to your breeze home!
descriptionHtml:
Whiterun home not big enough! 

Feature\'s.

Lots of stuff in the house. Outside the house has an enchanting table and alchemy table behind the house. Chair and chest infront.


WARNING!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
The cupboard missing in the screenshot that is normally in the house, Has been deleted for this update, if you have anything in it you may want to move it before installing this.

Also the weapon cases in the basement some have been removed so make sure you grab whatever you want to keep out of those cases and the weapon wall mount.

There is a master chest, with a surprise inside.

npc\'s should have no trouble walking around, I often find lydia in the basement sitting on MY THRONE, (whats she trying to say?) or eating bread.

May have a future update.
author: Rawvik
